flowchart LR
    A[Ingest folder] --> B[Discover files]
    B --> C{Any files?}
    C -- No --> Z[Stop]
    C -- Yes --> D[Summarize file into note]
    D --> E[Compose sections + components]
    E --> F[Embed section and components]
    F --> G{Similar section found?}
    G -- Yes --> H[LLM review decide merge or keep]
    G -- No --> I[Create new section]
    H --> J[Upsert section + components]
    I --> J
    J --> K[Save indexes]
    K --> L[Done]

    U[(Usage tracking)] -. summarize compose review embed .-> D
